    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#F2F2F2">
         <tr>
          <td style="padding: 50px; background-color: #fff; font-size: 16px;">
           <p><img src="https://s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/nomofomo-assets/emails/square-logo+copy.png" alt="Nomo_FOMO_logo" width="92" height="92" align="topright"></p>
            <h4 style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Roboto', serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0;">Hi <%= @user[:name] || 'there' %>,</h4>

            <p>Welcome to the Nomo FOMO community - we’re thrilled to have you on board! Just by signing up you’ve taken the first step towards strengthening your relationships while on the road.</p>

            <p>Here are three important steps for making the most of your Nomo FOMO experience:</p>

              <h4 style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Roboto', serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0;">1. Forward Us Your Confirmation Emails</h4>
              <p style="margin-top: 5px;">Simply forward all your accommodation, transportation, and event confirmation emails to <a href="mailto:rsvp@nomo-fomo.com">rsvp@nomo-fomo.com</a> and we’ll add them to your account for you!</p>

              <h4 style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Roboto', serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0;">2. Expand Your Network</h4>
              <p style="margin-top: 5px;">Invite your friends, family, and professional network to join you so that you never miss an opportunity to meet up. The more friends you have on Nomo FOMO + the more trips everyone enters = More chances for epic adventures!</p>

              <h4 style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Roboto', serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0;">3. Help Us Make This Your Ultimate Social Travel Network</h4>
              <p style="margin-top: 5px;">We would love to hear back from you with any new features ideas, bugs, or just to chat! Just reply to this email to directly talk with us or check out our <a href= "https://trello.com/b/ALkK1bMt/nomo-fomo-roadmap">Public Roadmap</a> to see the cool new features we are planning on rolling out.</p>
              <p></p>
              <%= link_to 'Log In', "https://www.nomo-fomo.com?utm_source=auto_email&utm_campaign=welcome", { style: 'width: 200px; height: 25px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #ef6045; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: white; display: inline-block; padding-top: 7px; padding-bottom: 10px;', target: :_blank } %>

            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for joining,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-family: 'Kaushan Script', cursive; margin-bottom: 0;">The Nomo FOMO Team</p>
            <p style="font-style: italic;">Building you your ultimate social travel network</p>
